race.comment: Tricky and the betting moves will be instructive. ENERGETIC (6) placed in a Belmont trial and then placed this track and trip much improved. She was expected to need the outing and is sure to be better for it. Races forward and has a fitness edge. CHE FIGATA (3) placed at Belmont his only run last preparation and pulled up with an issue. Started $2.5 and he's back after 239 days. Owns a solid Belmont trial with Pike aboard and Chris Parnham is reunited today. The gate is awkward, but he's talented and likely to race well. DOOR BUSTER (13) debuts and looked good winning a recent trial at Belmont. Has to be kept onside. JEMCONI (14) debuts and Pike is a key jockey booking. Has trialled at Belmont and the market will tell plenty with her.
